Name: Classic Jigsaw Puzzles
About the game: Classic Jigsaw Puzzles - Do puzzle in a new puzzle way! Advanced puzzle layout and involving game play will help you to relax after a hard-working day. Classic Jigsaw Puzzles is designed for adults and for kids. - 5 difficulty settings: Up to 280 pieces! - Every puzzle is unique: Different piece shapes every time! - Saves all puzzles in progress, so you can work on several at the same time. - 1080p HD Graphics. - Support multiple screen sizes.
